            <title>[SOLR-3641] CoreContainer is not persisting roles core attribute.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-3641</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;CoreContainer has some suspicious code that &lt;b&gt;reads&lt;/b&gt; &quot;roles&quot; attribute from solr.xml, but doesn&apos;t ever seem to write it back.&lt;/p&gt;

